     <h0>About <em>Credibl.com</em></h0>
      <p><em>CREDibl.com</em> publishes consumer and expert reviews for thousands of companies and products around the country. But we're not just another review website! We moderate every review and comment published on our website. In fact, we verify many of our reviews! We encourage all of our reviewers to submit supporting documentation to verify that they purchased the product or service they are revieweing. Although any registered user can submit a review or comment we only publish those which are well written and reflect the opinion of our readership in general. We believe that our review system is fair and helpful and we hope that you agree.</p>
      <p>Every review on <em>CREDibl.com</em> is easy-to-read, with large, obvious grades and keywords. And many of our reviews feature large, high-resolution photographs and slideshows. We want you to get the information you want quickly and easily!</p>
      <p>We appreciate readers who submit well written reviews and comments. Loyal reviewers can earn <em>honoraria</em> including:</p>
       <ul>
        <li>&bull; gift certificates</li>
        <li>&bull; swag</li>
        <li>&bull; and even cash!</li>
       </ul>
      <p>Please <a href="register.html">register today</a> or <a href="contact.html">contact us</a> with your questions. We love hearing from you!</p>
